Artificial Intelligence, AI, Machine Learning, Google DeepMind, OpenAI, ChatGPT, Anthropic, Tech, Coding, AI News, Large Language Models and... (most importantly)... optimism.

The  hussle would be hard to detect, and could easily be dangerous when the real weather turn, the weather services updates, but the intermediate (and cheaper) husselers don't actually update their data before a day has passed.
